      "content": "hey quick question... im taking sertraline for my mood but finals week is coming up and i feel super low and drained. i was thinking about adding some st johns wort to my routine to help boost things naturally since the sertraline is a bit mild for me. is that okay to do together or is there a problem with mixing them?",
